# Netflix Data Analysis Project

## Project Overview

This project analyzes the Netflix Movies and TV Shows dataset using Excel and Power BI to uncover insights about content distribution, release trends, genres, and ratings.

---

## Tools Used

- Microsoft Excel
- Power BI
- Data Cleaning
- Pivot Tables
- Dashboard Design
- Data Visualization

---

## Dataset Description

The dataset contains information about Netflix titles including:

- Title
- Type (Movie/TV Show)
- Director
- Cast
- Country
- Release Year
- Rating
- Duration
- Genre

---

## Key Questions Answered

- What type of content dominates Netflix?
- Which countries produce the most Netflix content?
- What are the most common genres?
- How has Netflix content changed over time?
- Which ratings are most common?

---

## Key Insights

### 1. Content Type Distribution
Movies dominate the Netflix catalog compared to TV Shows.

### 2. Release Year Trends
Netflix content increased significantly after 2015.

### 3. Country Analysis
The United States contributes the highest number of titles.

### 4. Genre Analysis
Drama and International Movies are among the most common genres.

### 5. Rating Distribution
TV-MA is the most frequently assigned rating.

